<div class="container">
   <section class="hero">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>At Chessy.gg, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your data when you use our platform.</p>
     <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> 23.12.2024</p>
  </section>
  
    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>1. Data Collection</h2>
      <p>We only collect the following information from users who log in via Discord:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Discord User ID</li>
        <li>Discord Username</li>
        <li>Discord Avatar (optional)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>These details are required to create your account and enable you to access Chessy.gg's features.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <p>Your data is solely used for the following purposes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Authenticating your account via Discord</li>
        <li>Providing access to Chessy.gg features</li>
        <li>Storing your game history, ELO ratings, and achievements</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not share your personal information with any third parties. Your data is exclusively used within the Chessy.gg platform to provide and enhance your experience.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>4. Analytics</h2>
      <p>Chessy.gg does not use any analytics tools or track your activity beyond the essential features of the platform.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>5. Security</h2>
      <p>We take reasonable measures to secure your data and prevent unauthorized access. However, please note that no system is completely foolproof, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request the deletion of your account and associated data</li>
        <li>Access and update your personal information</li>
        <li>Withdraw your consent to data usage</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at Discord via our Support Channel or at <a href="mailto:support@chessy.gg">support@chessy.gg</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </section>
</div>


